908 A.2d 1220 ATTORNEY GRIEVANCE COMMISSION OF MARYLAND, Petitioner, v. Charles F. WILHELM, Respondent. Misc. Docket AG No. 46,

Sept. Term, 2006.

Court of Appeals of Maryland. Oct. 11, 2006.

ORDER

This matter came before the Court on the Joint Petition for Placement on Inactive Status. Upon consideration of said petition, it is this 11th day of October, 2006,

ORDERED, that the Respondent Charles F. Wilhelm, be, and he is hereby placed on inactive status until further Order of this Court, and it is further,

ORDERED, that the Clerk of this Court shall remove the name of Charles F. Wilhelm from the register of attorneys in this Court until further Order of this Court and shall certify that fact to the Client Protection Fund and the Clerks of all judicial tribunals in this State in accordance with Maryland Rule 16-772(d).
